<h1><a name="Content">Private Events</a></h1>
<p class="goldBold">We can provide a service to suit your needs ranging from a meting in the house,family celebration to a dinner and dance using a marquee in the grounds.&nbsp; For larger parties the marqee can accommodate any size from 60 - 200.</p>
