<div id="accordion">
<h3><a href="#">Capacity</a></h3>
<div>
<p>Ardington House can host events in the main rooms of the House, and also in the extensive grounds. Drinks can be served on both the North and South manicured lawns, the island, marquee or lakeside.</p>
<p>For functions in the House alone, the main rooms can comfortably accommodate 150 standing guests. Seating capacity is 56 guests. Larger parties can be catered for in the Marquee.</p>
<p>The House is surrounded by magnificent gardens and grounds, including a picturesque lake which in the evenings is flood lit along with the House.</p>
<p>The catering services at Ardington House are exceptional <a href="#Catering">...Please click on catering to read more</a></p>
</div>
<h3><a name="Catering">Catering</a></h3>
<div>
<p>The catering services at Ardington House are exceptional and maintained to the highest possible standard. We are able to serve a full banquet, three-course meal, infomal buffet or simply canapes with the reception drinks.</p>
</div>
<h3><a href="#">Wines and Champagnes</a></h3>
<div>
<p>We offer Bauget-Jouette Champagne which has outsatnding value for a champagne with good body, bounce and a delicate bouquet.</p>
<p>Our wine list offers a tempting range of outstanding wines to suit all palates</p>
</div>
<h3><a href="#">Accommodation</a></h3>
<div>
<p>Some of your party may wish to stay at Ardington House. We have nine double/twin rooms. Extra may be available on request.</p>
<p>We will also be happy to provide details of local hotels, inns and B &amp; B's in the area.</p>
<p>Milton Mill House Hotel 01235 831474 is a short drive away and can provide additional accommodation at preferential rates.</p>
</div>
